The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to identify factual information and check its veracity in community question answering forums. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
